{"id":25,"date":"2023-06-23T18:39:29","date_gmt":"2023-06-23T18:39:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/storybook.spectator.co.uk\/?p=25"},"modified":"2023-07-18T16:05:57","modified_gmt":"2023-07-18T16:05:57","slug":"french-cave-markings-may-be-the-oldest-known-engravings-by-neanderthals","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/storybook.spectator.co.uk\/news\/french-cave-markings-may-be-the-oldest-known-engravings-by-neanderthals\/","title":{"rendered":"French cave markings may be the oldest known engravings by Neanderthals"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7lmxom000p87p376j1ahr0@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">Made by dragging fingers across relatively soft rock, lines, swirls and dots on the walls of a cave in France are the oldest known engravings by Neanderthals, according to a new analysis of the ancient marks.<\/p>\n<div class=\"related-content related-content--article\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/related-content\/instances\/clj7m4dgf00573b6fe2k2f2tj@published\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">\n<div class=\"related-content__image image__related-content\">\n<div class=\"image image__hide-placeholder image--eq-extra-small\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/image\/instances\/thumbnail-5610891e4960873f119c661fe7bb106d@published\" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-name=\"02 Neanderthal family tree\" data-component-name=\"image\" data-observe-resizes=\"\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300}\" data-original-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-original-height=\"1125\" data-original-width=\"2000\" data-url=\"https:\/\/media.cnn.com\/api\/v1\/images\/stellar\/prod\/221018133849-02-neanderthal-family-tree.jpg?c=original\" data-editable=\"settings\">\n<div class=\"image__container \" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300, &quot;image--show-credits&quot;: 596}\"><picture class=\"image__picture\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"image__dam-img\" src=\"https:\/\/media.cnn.com\/api\/v1\/images\/stellar\/prod\/221018133849-02-neanderthal-family-tree.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_144,w_256,c_fill\" alt=\"A reconstruction of a Neanderthal father and his daughter. \" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" \/><\/picture><\/div>\n<div class=\"image__metadata\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"related-content__headline\"><span class=\"related-content__headline-text\" data-editable=\"content.headline\">Ancient DNA reveals first Neanderthal family portrait<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7ltadg001i3b6fq4jffnyy@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">A team of researchers, led by Jean-Claude Marquet of the University of Tours in France, believe the markings \u201cdemonstrate a deliberate creative process,\u201d\u00a0the study published in the journal PLOS ONE\u00a0on Wednesday noted.<\/p>\n<div class=\"ad-slot-dynamic ad-slot-dynamic--1\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/ad-slot-dynamic\/instances\/sharethrough@published\" data-placement=\"{&quot;mobile&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:5},&quot;desktop&quot;:{&quot;position&quot;:3}}\" data-unselectable=\"true\">\n<div class=\"ad-slot\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/ad-slot\/instances\/cnn-v1@published\" data-path=\"end\/ad-slot-dynamic[0]\/items\" data-desktop-slot-id=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" data-mobile-slot-id=\"ad_nat_btf_01\" data-unselectable=\"true\">\n<div class=\"ad-slot__feedback ad-feedback-link-container\">\n<div class=\"ad-slot__ad-label\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7ltadh001j3b6fx328u8jn@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">\u201cThe traces preserved in the cave of La Roche-<a href=\"https:\/\/messi.online.mills.edu\/\">Cotard make a new<\/a> and very important contribution to our knowledge of Neanderthal behaviour,\u201d the study concluded.<\/p>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7ltadh001k3b6fj90ejj4s@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">The finding adds to a\u00a0growing body of evidence that Neanderthals\u00a0\u2014 who have been characterized as dim-witted cave dwellers \u2014 were creative beings and more complex than the stereotype suggests.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"neanderthals-deliberate-composition\" class=\"subheader\" data-editable=\"text\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/subheader\/instances\/clj7ltjad001x3b6fncy3fkkd@published\" data-component-name=\"subheader\">Neanderthals\u2019 \u2018deliberate composition\u2019<\/h3>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7lu0qg00263b6f0ln4wpce@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">To understand how the markings were made and whether they were intentional, the researchers made detailed 3D models of the engravings from photographs of the Loire Valley\u2019s La Roche-Cotard cave using a process known as photogrammetry.<\/p>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7lugz3002f3b6f50nmwybr@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">At the same time, the team conducted experiments in a nearby cavity dug out from the same type of rock 300 to 400 years ago. Researchers created similar marks on the wall \u2014 using bone, wood, antlers, flint and metal points, in addition to their fingers \u2014 and made similar 3D models from those, too.<\/p>\n<div class=\"image image__hide-placeholder image--eq-extra-small image--eq-small\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/image\/instances\/clj7m1xrl004x3b6fqi68x98q@published\" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-name=\"02 France cave engravings neanderthal scn\" data-component-name=\"image\" data-observe-resizes=\"\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300}\" data-original-ratio=\"0.561447286338116\" data-original-height=\"900\" data-original-width=\"1603\" data-url=\"https:\/\/media.cnn.com\/api\/v1\/images\/stellar\/prod\/230622130310-02-france-cave-engravings-neanderthal-scn.jpg?c=original\" data-editable=\"settings\">\n<div class=\"image__container \" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300, &quot;image--show-credits&quot;: 596}\"><picture class=\"image__picture\"><source srcset=\"https:\/\/media.cnn.com\/api\/v1\/images\/stellar\/prod\/230622130310-02-france-cave-engravings-neanderthal-scn.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_720,w_1280,c_fill\/f_webp\" type=\"image\/webp\" media=\"(min-width: 1280px)\" \/><source srcset=\"https:\/\/media.cnn.com\/api\/v1\/images\/stellar\/prod\/230622130310-02-france-cave-engravings-neanderthal-scn.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_540,w_960,c_fill\/f_webp\" type=\"image\/webp\" media=\"(min-width: 960px)\" \/><source srcset=\"https:\/\/media.cnn.com\/api\/v1\/images\/stellar\/prod\/230622130310-02-france-cave-engravings-neanderthal-scn.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_270,w_480,c_fill\/f_webp\" type=\"image\/webp\" media=\"(-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2)\" \/><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"image__dam-img\" src=\"https:\/\/media.cnn.com\/api\/v1\/images\/stellar\/prod\/230622130310-02-france-cave-engravings-neanderthal-scn.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_720,w_1280,c_fill\" alt=\"Examples of the engravings include a circular panel (left) with ogive-shaped tracings and a wavy panel with two contiguous tracings forming sinuous lines.\" width=\"1603\" height=\"900\" \/><\/picture><\/div>\n<div class=\"image__metadata\">\n<div class=\"image__caption attribution\"><span class=\"inline-placeholder\" data-editable=\"metaCaption\">Examples of the engravings include a circular panel (left) with ogive-shaped tracings and a wavy panel with two contiguous tracings forming sinuous lines.<\/span><\/div>\n<p>JC Marquet<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7lugz4002g3b6f2z3ac8iq@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">They used the information and measurements they gathered to distinguish the different types of marks visible on the Loire Valley cave walls and determine whether they were made by animals or humans and if they were ancient or made since 1912, when the cave was first excavated.<\/p>\n<div class=\"related-content related-content--article\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/related-content\/instances\/clj7m5iky005r3b6fdoxiy941@published\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">\n<div class=\"related-content__image image__related-content\">\n<div class=\"image image__hide-placeholder image--eq-extra-small\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/image\/instances\/thumbnail-19be4a79364456c5357cf3a8ad8f3a85@published\" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-name=\"01 neanderthal elephant hunting RE-UP\" data-component-name=\"image\" data-observe-resizes=\"\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300}\" data-original-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-original-height=\"1125\" data-original-width=\"2000\" data-url=\"https:\/\/media.cnn.com\/api\/v1\/images\/stellar\/prod\/230202121042-01-neanderthal-elephant-hunting-re-up.jpg?c=original\" data-editable=\"settings\">\n<div class=\"image__container \" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300, &quot;image--show-credits&quot;: 596}\"><picture class=\"image__picture\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"image__dam-img\" src=\"https:\/\/media.cnn.com\/api\/v1\/images\/stellar\/prod\/230202121042-01-neanderthal-elephant-hunting-re-up.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_144,w_256,c_fill\" alt=\"01 neanderthal elephant hunting RE-UP\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" \/><\/picture><\/div>\n<div class=\"image__metadata\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"related-content__headline\"><span class=\"related-content__headline-text\" data-editable=\"content.headline\">Neanderthals hunted massive elephants that once roamed northern Europe<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7lugz4002h3b6fya60hdlp@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">Based on the shape, spacing and arrangement of these engravings, the team concluded that markings in eight panels in La Roche-Cotard cave were intentional shapes and patterns created by human hands.<\/p>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7lugz4002i3b6faed8fss0@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">Most of the patterns, known as finger flutings, were made by fingers laid flat, with a few made by the edge of a finger. Six of the panels were at an average height of 1.5 to 1.7 meters (4.9 to 5.6 feet) above the floor.<\/p>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7lugz4002j3b6fw6rrvm8p@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">The finger flutings would have been much deeper and less precise if they were being used to collect rock powder for some purpose, the researchers said.<\/p>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7lugz4002k3b6fdhy01xxt@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">Instead, they believed the eight panels formed \u201ca seemingly organised set on the longest and most regular wall away from the cave entrance\u201d and that the layout of these graphic, nonfigurative designs on the wall of the cave was a \u201cdeliberate composition, and is the result of a thought process giving rise to conscious design and intent,\u201d according to the study.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"engravings-sealed-in-cave\" class=\"subheader\" data-editable=\"text\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/subheader\/instances\/clj7lwpz1003o3b6fcc1fqg9j@published\" data-component-name=\"subheader\">Engravings sealed in cave<\/h3>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7lwvod003x3b6fhgups95n@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">Researchers were not able to date the engravings directly, but \u2014 by using optically stimulated luminescence dating that measures when mineral in sediment was last exposed to sunlight \u2014 they estimated the marks were made at least 57,000 years ago when the cave became sealed off.<\/p>\n<div class=\"related-content related-content--article\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/related-content\/instances\/clj7mcq43006f3b6fcf2hls47@published\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">\n<div class=\"related-content__image image__related-content\">\n<div class=\"image image__hide-placeholder image--eq-extra-small\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/image\/instances\/thumbnail-57440307592759cde9095563600950f0@published\" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-name=\"02 prehistoric diets\" data-component-name=\"image\" data-observe-resizes=\"\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300}\" data-original-ratio=\"0.75\" data-original-height=\"1500\" data-original-width=\"2000\" data-url=\"https:\/\/media.cnn.com\/api\/v1\/images\/stellar\/prod\/221122082138-02-prehistoric-diets.jpg?c=original\" data-editable=\"settings\">\n<div class=\"image__container \" data-image-variation=\"image\" data-breakpoints=\"{&quot;image--eq-extra-small&quot;: 115, &quot;image--eq-small&quot;: 300, &quot;image--show-credits&quot;: 596}\"><picture class=\"image__picture\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"image__dam-img\" src=\"https:\/\/media.cnn.com\/api\/v1\/images\/stellar\/prod\/221122082138-02-prehistoric-diets.jpg?c=16x9&amp;q=h_144,w_256,c_fill\" alt=\"A view of Shanidar Cave in northern Iraq.\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" \/><\/picture><\/div>\n<div class=\"image__metadata\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"related-content__headline\"><span class=\"related-content__headline-text\" data-editable=\"content.headline\">Neanderthals cooked meals with pulses 70,000 years ago<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7lxenl00463b6fifk72u3t@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"on\">This date,<strong>\u00a0<\/strong>combined with the fact that all stone tools within the cave are Mousterian, a style associated with Neanderthals, is strong evidence that these engravings are the work of the extinct Stone Age hominin, according to the study.<\/p>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7lxenl00473b6fj2bh2m61@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\">Neanderthals are considered separate from Homo sapiens, our species, but they are from a close branch of the human family tree. The two groups overlapped in Europe for thousands of years, intermingled and had babies before Neanderthals became extinct. Most people alive today have traces of Neanderthal DNA.<\/p>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7lxenl00483b6fum7mm6sb@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\">The earliest widely accepted evidence of Homo sapiens in Europe dates from 45,500 years ago in Bulgaria, the study authors noted, although more recent discoveries suggest that\u00a0humans might have been in France even earlier.<\/p>\n<p class=\"paragraph inline-placeholder\" data-uri=\"cms.cnn.com\/_components\/paragraph\/instances\/clj7lxenl00493b6f4vgmye40@published\" data-editable=\"text\" data-component-name=\"paragraph\" data-analytics-observe=\"off\">Whether Neanderthals had an artistic sensibility has long been debated. At some cave sites in Spain, there\u2019s evidence \u2014 albeit contentious \u2014\u00a0that Neanderthals created abstract motifs and hand stencils.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Made by dragging fingers across relatively soft rock, lines, swirls and dots on the walls of a cave in France are the oldest known engravings by Neanderthals, according to a new analysis of the ancient marks. Ancient DNA reveals first Neanderthal family portrait A team of researchers, led by Jean-Claude Marquet of the University of<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/storybook.spectator.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/storybook.spectator.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/storybook.spectator.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/storybook.spectator.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/storybook.spectator.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=25"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/storybook.spectator.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":170,"href":"https:\/\/storybook.spectator.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/25\/revisions\/170"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/storybook.spectator.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=25"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/storybook.spectator.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=25"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/storybook.spectator.co.uk\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=25"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}